                            turnaround activities</li>
                        <li><?php echo $name; ?> provide engineering solutions for particularly difficult lifting
                            operations which
                            require technical support to ensure a safe system of work is achieved</li>
                        <li><?php echo $name; ?> also provide the provision of inspection services including all lifting
                            appliances
                            and accessories utilised in all areas of the project, as well as the statute government
                            periodic inspections of client owned 'special equipment'</li>
                        <li>The lift supervisors check the training and competency standards of all national crane
                            operators, signallers, slingers and riggers on the CDB project.</li>
